product description:
The THERMAL O/L RELAY CL10, designed for
 current capacities ranging from 90-150A and 
compatible with D115/D150 applications, 
exemplifies Schneider Electric's dedication to 
delivering efficient motor protection solutions.
 Engineered with precision and reliability in 
mind, this thermal overload relay plays a 
crucial role in safeguarding electric motors 
within the specified current range.
